---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const title = "Entryway & Mudroom Cabinets: Furniture-Grade Storage by Klovo";
const description = "Klovo garage cabinets are designed with a furniture-grade TFL finish that looks appropriate in any room of your home — not just the garage. The clean aesthetic, soft-close hardware, and moisture-resistant construction make them ideal for mudrooms and entryways.";
---

<PageLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="page-hero page-hero--neutral">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">
      <span class="eyebrow">Entryway &amp; Mudroom</span>
      <h1 class="page-h1">{title}</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">
      <article class="prose-klovo">

        <p>Klovo garage cabinets are designed with a furniture-grade TFL finish that looks appropriate in any room of your home — not just the garage. The clean aesthetic, soft-close hardware, and moisture-resistant construction make them ideal for mudrooms and entryways where boots, coats, and seasonal gear need organized storage. The patent-pending GlideLock assembly system allows each cabinet to be assembled in approximately 2–3 minutes — almost tool-free — making a complete entryway transformation achievable in a single afternoon.</p>

        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions About Entryway &amp; Mudroom Cabinets</h2>

        <h3>Can Klovo garage cabinets be used in a mudroom or entryway?</h3>
        <p>Absolutely. Klovo cabinets are designed with a furniture-grade TFL finish that looks appropriate in any room of your home — not just the garage. The clean aesthetic, soft-close hardware, and moisture-resistant construction make them ideal for mudrooms and entryways.</p>

        <h3>How do I organize a mudroom with Klovo cabinets?</h3>
        <p>A typical mudroom setup uses a combination of tall cabinets for coats and boots, upper cabinets for hats/gloves/scarves, and base cabinets for shoes and bags. Klovo's modular system lets you mix and match cabinet sizes to fit your space and family's needs.</p>

        <h3>Will wet boots and coats damage Klovo cabinets?</h3>
        <p>Klovo's moisture-resistant TFL finish and PVC edge-banding are designed to handle the real-world conditions of a mudroom — including wet boots, damp coats, and seasonal humidity. For best results, allow very wet items to drip-dry briefly before storing.</p>

        <h3>How much space do I need for a mudroom cabinet setup?</h3>
        <p>Klovo's modular system starts at just 6 feet wide, making it suitable for narrow entryways and hallways. Vertical configurations with wall-mounted upper cabinets maximize storage without consuming floor space.</p>

        <h3>Are Klovo cabinets strong enough for heavy winter gear?</h3>
        <p>Yes. With 500 lbs per cabinet, Klovo cabinets easily handle heavy winter coats, snow boots, ski equipment, and other bulky seasonal gear.</p>

        <h2>Related Resources</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/pages/garage-cabinets">Garage Cabinet Systems &rarr;</a></li>
          <li><a href="/pages/laundry-room-cabinets">Laundry Room Cabinets &rarr;</a></li>
          <li><a href="/pages/diy-garage-cabinets">DIY Garage Cabinets &rarr;</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blogs/news/why-kitchen-grade-cabinets-belong-in-your-garage">Why Kitchen-Grade Cabinets Belong in Your Garage &rarr;</a></li>
        </ul>

      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style is:global>
.prose-klovo { font-family: var(--sans); color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.75; }
.prose-klovo h2 { font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(22px,2.8vw,30px); color: var(--ink); margin: 48px 0 16px; }
.prose-klovo h3 { font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 20px; color: var(--ink); margin: 36px 0 12px; }
.prose-klovo p { margin: 0 0 20px; }
.prose-klovo ul, .prose-klovo ol { padding-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.prose-klovo li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
.prose-klovo strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
.prose-klovo a { color: var(--amber); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }
.prose-klovo a:hover { color: var(--ink); }
.prose-klovo table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 24px 0; font-size: 15px; }
.prose-klovo th { background: var(--neutral); font-family: var(--display); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); padding: 10px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); text-align: left; }
.prose-klovo td { padding: 12px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); color: var(--ink-soft); }
.prose-klovo tbody tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
</style>
